12 An act relating to sharing the costs of electric grid upgrades
13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. COSTS OF ELECTRIC GRID UPGRADES; PUBLIC UTILITY
15 COMMISSION RULE
16 (a) On or before July 1, 2026, the Public Utility Commission shall adopt by
17 rule standards and procedures for ensuring that the costs of any improvements
18 or upgrades to the electric transmission and distribution grid in a utility’s
19 service territory are shared as fairly and as evenly as possible among all
20 ratepayers in the utility’s service territory.
